Package: synthvisium
Type: Package
Title: synthvisium is a package to generate synthetic Visium-like spot data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: person("Robin", "Browaeys", email = "robin.browaeys@ugent.be",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Robin Browaeys <robin.browaeys@ugent.be>
Description: synthvisium is a package to generate synthetic Visium-like spot data. 
    It works by making mixtures of cells that are provided in the input scRNAseq data.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
URL: https://github.com/browaeysrobin/synthvisium
BugReports: https://github.com/browaeysrobin/synthvisium/issues
